---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="solution" background="dark">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-16">I do things differently</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="text-left">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-blue) 0%, var(--color-accent-blue-dark) 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: var(--color-dark-bg); line-height: 1;">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">Strategy</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          I embed as your GTM leader and build your strategy - ICP, positioning, segmentation, channels. The foundational work most startups skip.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-left">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-blue) 0%, var(--color-accent-blue-dark) 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: var(--color-dark-bg); line-height: 1;">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">Playbook</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Then I create the playbook - your sales process, messaging frameworks, objection handling, discovery questions, competitive positioning. The actual words your team needs to win deals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-left">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-blue) 0%, var(--color-accent-blue-dark) 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: var(--color-dark-bg); line-height: 1;">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Then I build it into AI infrastructure - intelligent agents trained on YOUR playbook that your team can access 24/7 through your AI platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card max-w-4xl mx-auto relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-accent-blue) 0%, var(--color-accent-blue-dark) 100%);"></div>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; padding-left: 2rem;">
        The strategy becomes a playbook. The playbook becomes infrastructure. <span class="gradient-text">The infrastructure stays after I leave.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
